{"word":"H7663 - שָׂבַר - sâbar - saw-bar' - Hope","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׂבַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>sâbar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>saw-bar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Hope"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - காத்திரு, பார்வையிடு, நோக்கி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to inspect, to examine, to wait, to hope, to wait upon"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) examined (participle)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to wait (for), to wait upon"},{"paragraph":"2) to hope (for)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> The second form being used erroneously in Neh 2:13, Neh 2:15; a primitive root; to <i>scrutinize</i>; by implication (of <i>watching</i>) to <i>expect</i> (with hope and patience): - hope, tarry, view, wait."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7663 - שָׂבַר - sâbar - saw-bar'/7663\">H7663</a>, <a href=\"#/H7664 - שֵׂבֶר - sêber - say'-ber/7664\">H7664</a>"}]}